# RankR â€“ Real-Time Poll App

RankR is a real-time ranked-choice poll application built with a modern tech stack. Users can create polls, vote on nominations, and see results instantly. This project combines a React frontend, Node.js backend, and PostgreSQL database, all containerized with Docker for easy deployment.

